# The app lives on nicespaceship.ai. If a user lands on
# nicespaceship.com/app/* (typo, stale link, confusion between .com and .ai),
# 301 them to the same path on the app domain instead of falling through to
# the marketing site's index.html (which silently returns the home page).

/app   https://nicespaceship.ai/app/         301
/app/  https://nicespaceship.ai/app/         301
/app/* https://nicespaceship.ai/app/:splat   301
